data.description: Welcome to Remington Ridge! Fall in love with this charming 3-bed, 2-bath ranch-style home on a corner lot that welcomes you with an abundance of natural light throughout. Skylights in the living room enhance the brightness, while the kitchen features stainless steel appliances, white cabinets, and updated hardware. The owner's suite boasts an updated bathroom, and a partially finished basement provides versatile space, including ample room for storage. Conveniently, the laundry is located on the entry level for added ease and accessibility. Enjoy modern living in a thoughtfully designed residence. Plus, benefit from Columbus taxes and Groveport schools, adding to the appeal of this delightful home. Showings will begin 02/22/24! You're not going to want to miss out on this home!
